Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照射黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說 促使宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方 呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.82,0:00:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.69,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡為此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.43,0:00:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換取持續戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.77,0:00:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為命運而不知所措之\N嘆息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因無法抹去的記憶\N而為愛顫抖著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當月光照亮黑夜之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說促使得宇宙舞動著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的墜天使們啊\N美麗的飛翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的決鬥展開時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.74,0:01:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遙遠的地方呼喊著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刪除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將所有的人類...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.83,0:01:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的存在...刪除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探測出他們的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因應該區域的條件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用最佳的方法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刪除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭遇障礙時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對應該條件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.98,0:01:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用最佳的方法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.25,0:01:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排除障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該命令效期...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.98,0:02:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.73,0:02:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼超重機組們的機體\N全都遍體鱗傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.26,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的進化比\N桑德曼先生預測的還要快嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果進化目的只是要屠殺人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要這種破壞力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.33,0:02:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種是為了\N對付超重神而展開進化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了、不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快想辦法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊這個就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十三話 白銀之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦不過是\N總統親臨的公開發表會而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒備還真是森嚴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是四木重工的直昇機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍需品公司也相當感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對外星異種用的機動組件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣的機械啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:04:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我們的戰鬥機\N會變得可以變形、合體呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.94,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後變成像超重神\N那種巨型的機械人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想坐上去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本的作業\N請依照指導手冊去進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後媚月小姐跟莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在反電磁力場產生裝置\N開始運轉時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請檢查電裝系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上次的踢腿後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.47,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G攻擊機的合神部分的軸組\N跟裝甲的負荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠的超過了\N耐久基準數值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要仔細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並接受朵莉雅的指示來作檢查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.25,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的又不是我踢的\N是斗牙踢的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不都是因為你沒考慮到後果\N亂踢一通的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠多考慮一下\N重鑽機的迴轉方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟推送軸的運動能量的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不都是因為妳沒考慮到後果\N亂鑽一通的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位請不要吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啦\N什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對、對不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸的氣息完全一致呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個真是相親相愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會跟這種女人...\N誰會跟這種東西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情形下\N真的能修得完嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題我們也會加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛娜一起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.67,0:05:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對準人類、地球的侵略者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天比一天強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們EFA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了地球真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.90,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的力量現在正式誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦這個不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來相當具有廣用性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實戰的配備從什麼時候開始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的體型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅曾報告說外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了徹底破壞超重神\N而展開了進化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.04,0:06:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許已經到了該把"那個"\N託付給我們的騎士之時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定要看清楚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.05,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定他們是否真的有足以\N被託付予白銀之牙的資格嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馳騁於天際
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛奔於海面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將主宰著宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便是我們EFA的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對外星異種用之機動組件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦差不多要登場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾力克斯隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從正上方\N有未確認部隊急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是隕石?不在減速中\N該不會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其名為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生緊急狀況!發生緊急狀況!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種出現在地球聯合政府大樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.63,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在當地進行迎擊的EFA空軍部隊\N以及地面部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已呈現毀滅狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統親臨的公開發表會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了空歡喜一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.68,0:09:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在外星異種\N處於完全靜默狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼這次的敵人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎外星異種比起屠殺人類\N反而更有興趣與我們的騎士決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時機剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓徹夜修理有了意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯大家都很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.68,0:09:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐您的臉色不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?沒事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最近老是睡不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.62,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼超重神都整修完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以迎擊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法許可各位迎擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為、為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為外星異種\N的目標是超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星異種...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以超重神為目標?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在第一次攻擊後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有活動跡象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠是在等待\N等著超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不應該避之不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方既然下了戰帖...\N 笨蛋好好想一想..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:11:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕對方已經進化到可以應付\N超重神所有的攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經進化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換句話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.49,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有足以造成\N那個外星異種損傷的武器嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕超重神武器的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.97,0:11:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不讓我們去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.24,0:11:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的戰鬥應該不是\N只為了我們自己的存亡而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠守護重要的人們或事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我們地球戰騎隊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是超重神所應進行的戰鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這時候畏懼不敢迎戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒有臉去見綾香了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行以超重神目前的裝備...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位武器的話這裡有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開發編號:XB-04
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試作型劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重萬斷劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然反應上有些許難處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但破壞力可稱得上削鐵如泥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀身上的耐重力子結晶塗裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也在武裝班的成員\N努力下完美地完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致上所有的敵人\N都可以一刀兩斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帥啊! 太帥了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒話說了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要出發囉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外觀有點粗糙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武風與流線所形成的丰姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀身寧靜的光輝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及眾人灌注於這把劍中的\N意念力量之強大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願為此劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及吾等諸位騎士們的勇氣\N而放手一搏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出擊迎戰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有機體檢查完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G要塞隨時都可以出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右邊的三個人\N要乖乖的坐好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的作戰目的有二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一個目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.73,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摧毀攻擊地球聯合政府大樓\N的外星異種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而第二個目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准有任何一個例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要平安歸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神GRAVION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出動!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要以最高速度出發囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你... 不去避難嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是最棒的特等席不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是超重神失敗的話\N躲到哪裡都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此即使只是多一秒鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都要留在\N我最鍾愛的研究對象身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在所能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有為他們祈求勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此\N就讓我在此看盡一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.04,0:14:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他們是不是\N真的是人類的希望所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 到達指定地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G戰騎的各位\N立刻進入作戰行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最高加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.49,0:14:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓超重神一直衝到\N超過敵人的預測速度範圍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺、媚月小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\NOK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.37,0:15:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後用遠遠超過\N敵人預測的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺揮劍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G萬斷劍在剛剛的衝擊下\N已經無法再撐下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請快出擊毀掉牠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G萬斷劍鋒利度提升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠打算幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學終結!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飛彈萬彈齊發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連G萬斷劍都沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.66,0:16:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道超重神的裝備\N就到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是現在的他們\N應該能負擔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重毒蛇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要、要輸了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起來琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒有輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...一起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不會有要輸的感覺了呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是挺行的嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是超重劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是超重劍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是把能開拓出人類未來的牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工學暴風!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超! 重! 斷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.83,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連攻擊對象的空間\N都一起一刀兩斷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操控重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還連空間都征服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.31,0:20:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也得儘早\N讓我們的王牌完成才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.51,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了! 立花少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經盡力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一回到城裡\N就馬上幫你修好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們也都表現的不錯呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要戰鬥多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才能帶我去見綾香啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡、悔恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人無論在哪個時代\N都不斷在重複著相同的錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那群年輕人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以跨越我們的愚昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不敢寄望\N他們能夠理解我們的罪過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當這一切都結束的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將到妳的身邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.72,0:21:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著在烈陽熱氣下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.23,0:21:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈現形形色色的擺動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.27,0:21:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知該為何這般\N心頭思緒紛亂不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就這麼視而不見\N朝向明日飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.86,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才說出了這麼不客氣的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.23,0:22:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤單一人地強出頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.14,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換來的只有誤解\N矛盾與迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.94,0:22:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於那牽繫著悲傷的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.18,0:22:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓微笑的雙眸中滲出了淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.68,0:22:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想將這暖意傳送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.49,0:22:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便緊握著手一直不願放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好讓這祈禱得以傳達